In the console type;

sudo X -configure

then 

nvidia-settings

Configure your monitor(s) settings.
click apply and then "Save to X conifiguration file"

Click Show Preview and copy the text that shows up.

> Next navigate to /etc/X11/ and open xorg.conf

Now replace the contents of it with the ones we copied from nvidia-settings and save it. 
'Kate' ( KDE's Text Editor ) will ask for your password to allow the file to be overwritten.

Done!
